            "notes": "The main concept of this deck is to utilize Brigid, Clachan's Heart as the commander to lead an aggressive strategy focused on deploying efficient creatures and generating value through various synergies. The deck includes a mix of mana dorks, utility creatures, and powerful spells to support Brigid's ability to control the board and pressure opponents. With cards like Birthing Pod, Survival of the Fittest, and various tutor effects, the deck aims to consistently find key pieces and maintain a proactive game plan. Additionally, the inclusion of protective spells like Giver of Runes and removal options like Swords to Plowshares helps to ensure Brigid's survival and the deck's ability to maintain tempo and pressure throughout the game."
